OL,3,C'Christmas miracle' as pub devastated
OL,4,Cby flooding reopens
OL,6,FA pub in Bath that was badly damaged
OL,7,Fby flooding following heavy rain and
OL,8,Fdownpours during Storm Bert has re-
OL,9,Fopened.
OL,11,FFive people and two dogs had to be
OL,12,Frescued by fire crews after becoming
OL,13,Ftrapped inside the Bathampton Mill, in
OL,14,FBath, when the River Avon burst its
OL,15,Fbanks at the end of November.
OL,17,FEmily Abbott, Deputy Manager at the
OL,18,FBathampton Mill, said the pub had to
OL,19,Fundergo extensive renovations but it
OL,20,Fis "fantastic" to be able to welcome
OL,21,Fcustomers back once again.
