OL,3,C'Christmas miracle' as pub devastated
OL,4,Cby flooding reopens
OL,6,F"I don't think there is anything worse
OL,7,Fthan a pub closed in the festive
OL,8,Fseason, so it's great to get the team
OL,9,Fback through the doors and get our
OL,10,Fguests back through the doors," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FMs Abbott, who lives above the pub,
OL,14,Fsaid she was expecting some damage as
OL,15,Fthe building has flooded before, but
OL,16,Fdidn't expect the water level to rise
OL,17,Fso quickly.
